   NAME
	SETKEYBOARD - Changes the keymap used by the current Amiga 
	              console.

   FORMAT
	SETKEYBOARD <keymap>

   TEMPLATE
	KEYMAP/A

   PATH
	C:SETKEYBOARD

   FUNCTION
	SETKEYBOARD specifies the keymap used by the Amiga for the
	current console. The keymap file must be present in KEYMAPS:
	for SETKEYBOARD to find it.

   EXAMPLES
	To change to a Canadian keymap, type:

	    1> SETKEYBOARD cdn
